item.title: Olivia Adriance: How To Make Healthy Food Fun, Pregnancy & Unsolicited Advice
item.description: Ep. 189: Just days before her due date, Olivia Adriance joins us to share what it’s really like being pregnant as a content creator. We break down the pressure to stay productive even during pregnancy and how she’s navigating unsolicited advice with more intention than ever.
